OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30210
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1778292207
OL,3,CStarmer refuses to shift 'left or
OL,4,Cright' amid pressure over electoral
OL,5,Cmauling
OL,7,F"I'll continue putting my shoulder to
OL,8,Fthe wheel as the Health and Social
OL,9,FCare Secretary, who's getting the NHS
OL,10,Fback on its feet and making sure it's
OL,11,Ffit for the future," he said.
OL,13,FKey developments after 127 of 136
OL,14,FEnglish councils had declared full
OL,15,Fresults are:
OL,17,F` Labour had lost control of 31
OL,18,Fcouncils and suffered a net loss of
OL,19,F1,022 seats.
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@TO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30211
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1778292207
OL,3,CStarmer refuses to shift 'left or
OL,4,Cright' amid pressure over electoral
OL,5,Cmauling
OL,7,F` Reform gained control of 12 councils
OL,8,Fand added 1,244 seats.
OL,10,F` The Conservatives suffered a net
OL,11,Floss of eight councils and 417
OL,12,Fcouncillors.
OL,14,F` The Liberal Democrats won three
OL,15,Fcouncils and gained a net 146 seats.
OL,17,F` The Green Party gained control of
OL,18,Ffour councils and put on 297
OL,19,Fcouncillors.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
