PN,30212
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1778292207
OL,3,CStarmer refuses to shift 'left or
OL,4,Cright' amid pressure over electoral
OL,5,Cmauling
OL,7,F` In Scotland, after 80 results out of
OL,8,F81 constituencies and regions, the SNP
OL,9,Fhad 57 seats, Labour 17, Reform 15,
OL,10,Fthe Scottish Greens 13, the
OL,11,FConservatives 11 and the Liberal
OL,12,FDemocrats nine.
OL,14,F` In Wales, Plaid Cymru have 43 seats
OL,15,Fin the Senedd, with Reform on 34,
OL,16,FLabour on nine, the Conservatives on
OL,17,Fseven, the Greens on two and the
OL,18,FLiberal Democrats on one.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/12
